  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then take your <strong>steak </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let it adjust to room temperature</p><p>Slice your<strong> potatoes </strong>(skins on) into discs, then add to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray (or two!) with your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and mix together</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and cooked through – these are your <strong>smoky potatoes</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/reuben-style-steak-sandwich-with-dill-pickles-and-smoky-potatoes/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate most of your <strong>radishes</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining radishes </strong>into quarters</p><p>Slice<strong> half </strong>your <strong>cucumber</strong> into rounds</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining cucumber</strong> into batons lengthways</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/reuben-style-steak-sandwich-with-dill-pickles-and-smoky-potatoes/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>grated radishes </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong>, <strong>diced shallot</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> and a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/reuben-style-steak-sandwich-with-dill-pickles-and-smoky-potatoes/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>dill </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add the <strong>radish quarters</strong> and <strong>cucumber rounds</strong> to a small bowl with the <strong>cucumber slices</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>chopped dill</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong>, then give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>dill, cucumber & radish pickles</strong> and <strong>quick-pickled cucumber rounds</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/reuben-style-steak-sandwich-with-dill-pickles-and-smoky-potatoes/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Pat your <strong>rump steak[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper, then drizzle them with <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>on both sides</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/reuben-style-steak-sandwich-with-dill-pickles-and-smoky-potatoes/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once very hot, add the <strong>steak[s]</strong> to the pan</p><p>For rare, cook for 2 min max on each side; for medium-rare, cook for 2-3 min on each side; for medium, cook for 3-4 min on each side</p><p>Once the <strong>steak</strong> is cooked, transfer to a clean chopping board to rest for 5 min</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/reuben-style-steak-sandwich-with-dill-pickles-and-smoky-potatoes/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 5 min or until hot and crusty</p><p>Carefully slice in half before serving</p><p>Once rested, slice the <strong>cooked steak</strong> as thinly as you can on a clean board</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/reuben-style-steak-sandwich-with-dill-pickles-and-smoky-potatoes/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stuff your <strong>hot ciabatta</strong> with the<strong> sliced steak</strong>, <strong>pickled radish slaw</strong> and the<strong> quick-pickled cucumber rounds</strong></p><p>Serve with the<strong> smoky potatoes </strong>and the<strong> dill, cucumber & radish pickles</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
